-- Russia says willing to invest $1 bln in Serbia's NIS oil company
-- By Ivana Sekularac
-- Thu Oct 16, 2014 08:24AM EDT
-- None



BELGRADE, Oct 16 (Reuters) - President Vladimir Putin said in Belgrade on Thursday that Russia was willing to invest $1 billion in Serbian oil company NIS <NIIS.BEL>, majority owned buy Russia's Gazpom Neft <SIBN.MM>.

